high_descs: Turn around, move forward, turn right, move forward for the fridge, turn right, move forward, then turn left to approach the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the cup in the right cabinet, above the counter.
Turn right, move forward then turn left to face the stove.
Warm the cup in the microwave, above the stove.
Turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the counter next to the stove.
Place the cup in the cabinet above the counter, to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup in the cabinet.

high_descs: Head to the counter next to the stove on the left.
Open the cabinet above and pick up the green cup from in there.
Bring the cup to the microwave on the right.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Bring the heated cup to the cabinet on the left next to the microwave.
Put the heated cup in the cabinet next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup in a cabinet.

high_descs: Go left and then right to stand in front of the cabinet to the left of the microwave.
Open the upper cabinet on the right and take out the green vase.
Go to the right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the vase in the microwave and turn it on and then take it out and shut the door.
Go left and face the cabinets to the left of the stove.
Open the upper cabinet, closest to the microwave, and put the vase in and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed vase in the cupboard.
